reviews.review_text: Kick ass show I was at this show, had what I thought were shitty seat on the upper deck...boy, was I wrong.  From the get go, they rocked the house.. I was afraid that the the upper deck was gonna collapse from the way it was swaying from everyone dancing their asses off. Also,  starting off with Eyes into Walkin' was unexpected.. Needless too say we had ourselves a real good time
